      "file_path": "controlloop/templates/template.demo.clc/src/test/java/org/onap/policy/template/demo/clc/SupportUtil.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 162,
      "message": "I think these new function methods should not be in src/test/ as they provides the actual functions to generate xacml policy using yaml values. According to our new api design, the coordination yaml here is the \"policy\" provided by client, analogous to operational policy yaml, and firstBlocksSecond.xml is the \"PolicyTypeImpl\", analogous to drools template. The new functions added here are typically for generating a \"PolicyImpl\" from a \"Policy\" and a \"PolicyTypeImpl\" according to the top figure https://wiki.onap.org/display/DW/Policy+Design+and+API+Flow+for+Model+Driven+Control+Loop+-+Draft \n\nPam, Liam, do I understand correctly?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 1441,
        "name": "Chenfei Gao",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "cgao@research.att.com",
        "username": "cgao"
      },
      "updated": "2019-02-21 02:44:31.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": null,
      "unresolved": false
